{"tid":2517582,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"4月強積金成員平均進帳5286元 兩大MPF龍頭擁最多冠軍基金","createTime":"2021-05-05T11:53:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T12:23:00.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9c20b02a0498e153d49101a0c9fc5b1199c9ea","tid":2517582,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2945000/2949722/050521_iet_patrick_mpf_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2945000%2F2949722%2F050521_iet_patrick_mpf_1024.jpg&h=1e226b8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民不時狠批强積金（MPF）「回報低、收費高」、尤其是巨無霸輸蝕給中小型受託人，<span class=\"red\">如今龍頭終於可以大平反，皆因MPF繼續為打工仔帶來創紀錄的財富</span>，據強積金專家、積金評級公司總結4月份的市况，全月強積金錄得240億元的投資收益。而10隻表現最佳的成分基金中，相信兩大霸主的捧場客最開心，因一哥宏利，以及市佔率排第2的滙豐（HSBC）及恒生（00011）為兩大赢家，佔其中七隻基金。<br />\n<br />\n積金評級剛發表4月份的強積金表現調查，4月份的強積金基金單月平均回報率為1.89％，強積金體系的總投資收益為235.7億元，而每名成員的平均投資收益估計為5,286元。若以人均帳戶來看，<span class=\"red\">平均帳戶結餘現時預計約達 267,521元</span>，創歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n至於強積金總資產，月內曾突破1.2萬億元的門檻後，預計<span class=\"red\">4月底強積金總資產約達1.197萬億港元</span>，創月底的歷史記錄。論及各類產品，4月份全部報捷，沒有任何強積金資產類別在4月份錄得負回報。另外，根據積金評級股票基金（美國）指數，美股基金連續第二個月成為表現最佳的強積金資產類別。<br />\n<br />\n而打工仔緊盯所揀MPF的投資成績，4月份的<span class=\"red\">十隻表現最佳的強積金成分基金中有八隻是美股基金</span>。宏利北美股票基金上月勁彈6.85%，滙豐及恒生的美國股票基金也上漲5.44%，不僅跑贏美股平均只升5.2%的回報，亦較所有MPF整體中位數僅錄得1.9%升幅為好。再者，中銀保誠及友邦（01299）的北美股票基金亦打入10大冠軍榜列，中小型服務商中，只得萬通的王牌產品、美股基金跑出。"},{"pid":"fb358c5949e9420f2997e538cc978815d47a5200","tid":2517582,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"美股又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df4b292eaba2be9325cf914cbf6fe51f0e841ff","tid":2517582,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"用緊宏利,今個月多左8千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fee0b441f111f30ef7d5d0803b986c4e1c1bd4f","tid":2517582,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb358c5949e9420f2997e538cc978815d47a5200","tid":2517582,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"美股又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"MPF十分反智<br />\n揸5成以上既保本基金手續費竟然可以收2%一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bee7d1e11fd361703556958c03e9e55e4c0bcdb","tid":2517582,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"MPF十分反智<br />\n揸5成<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">現金</span></span></strong>以上既保本基金手續費竟然可以收2%一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa13fadf94ec8fd82c716e4a04958466c8871973","tid":2517582,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb358c5949e9420f2997e538cc978815d47a5200","tid":2517582,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:02:19.000Z","msg":"美股又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"3月輸完一次，5月份又再輸一次啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係睇個4月把撚"},{"pid":"111b2becdfb571854136023a7510a4b7624b85da","tid":2517582,"uid":83654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T12:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcyReukXn4RV17inCFeoVAW7YfJtqBQPNrEQA2wAfzKgt?filename=1o5zOB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1o5zOB5.png&h=f58677b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美股今年都賺緊9皮野， <br />\n年底應該可以賺夠15萬 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}